erscore!). This will be used as a name of the formula variable connected with this field!'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Required?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Choose whether the user must fill out this field or not.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Type of field'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Choose the type based on type of data you are expecting from users. For instance, 
                if you expect some text or don\'t mind about type of data at all, choose type "string".'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'String'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Integer'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Decimals'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Minimum value'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add the minimum allowed value for this field. Only integer or float number.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Maximum value'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add the maximum allowed value for this field. Only integer or float number.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Step value'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add the step value for this field. Only integer or float number.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Default (initial) value'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add the default value for this field'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Min. number of characters'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add the minimum allowed number of characters for this field.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Max. number of characters'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add the maximum allowed number of characters for this field.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Price / Rate'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enter the price (or rate) for this field. This value can be used in a formula. 
                Or leave it blank if you need just an information added by the user.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Label text'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Custom text that will be used for this field as its title on the product page and as the cart/order item\'s option\'s title. Leave it blank and there will not be a title for this field and the option\'s slug will be used as a title for cart / order item'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Type of tag for label'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Label text in cart/order meta'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Custom text that will be used as a title for this option in cart/order item meta'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable tooltip?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enables/disables displaying of the tooltip'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Text for tooltip'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Custom text that will be used in tooltip.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Class name'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Extra selector from Popup Maker'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Type of tooltip'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Classic'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Lightbox'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Popup Maker'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Tooltip Image'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable inline editing in cart?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enables/disables a possibility to edit this option inline in the cart. Such possibility must also be enabled globally for this product.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable conditional logic?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enables conditional logic for displaying or hiding this module.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Show or hide by default?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Choose whether this option should be shown or hidden at the beginning,
                so its state will be changed to the opposite once the condition is met.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Hide'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Show'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Field conditional logic builder'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Sub options'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add some sub options for select and, please, keep unique slugs for them. These slugs might be used in a formula conditional rules (e.g. when you use operators "equal", "not equal" etc).'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add some sub options for this option and, please, keep unique slugs for them. These slugs might be used in a formula conditional rules (e.g. when you use operators "equal", "not equal" etc).'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Type of radio input'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Style of radio input'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Square'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Circle'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Uploading mode'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Choose whether it will be possible to upload only one file per option or many.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Single'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Multiple'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'This setting overrides similar global setting for this option only.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'A comma separated list of allowed mime types. This setting overrides similar global setting for this option only.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Type of checkbox input'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Colour'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Text'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Style of checkbox input'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable image changing?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enables the functionality of changing of the product main image upon selection in this option'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Custom validation messages'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enables an opportunity to set custom validation message for certain validation event. In case of the last field the format is: "data-parsley-`constraint`-message="my msg"'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Extra validation rules'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add new validation rules for this option'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable validation logic?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enables validation conditional logic for this option.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Conditional validation scheme'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Disable Calendar?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enables/disables datepicker functionality.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable Timepicker?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enables/disables timepicker functionality.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'24-hour Time Picker?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enables/disables calendar functionality.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Minimum time'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add the minimum/earliest time (inclusively) allowed for selection. You can use only 24-h format. For example: 09:00 or 19:00.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Maximum time'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add the maximum/latest time (inclusively) allowed for selection. You can use only 24-h format. For example: 09:00 or 19:00.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Minute increment'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Adjusts the step for the minute input'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Suboptions conditional rules'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Conditionally displaying suboptions'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Choose whether these suboptions should be shown or hidden at the beginning,
                so its state will be changed to the opposite once the condition is met.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Hide meta in cart/order details?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Hides this option related meta in cart/order details.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Mode'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Choose between using like a regular "add to cart" button or specifically for "free sample" functionality (marks cart item as "sample").'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Regular'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'"Free sample"'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'"Free sample" Mode'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Choose between adding "sample" with calculated price or set its price to zero regarding price calculation rules.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Calc price'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Zero price'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Origin Postcode'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Base postcode. In single mode serves as origin postcode. It is ignored in dual mode.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Single or dual mode'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'In "single" mode displays only one input field. In dual mode displays two, so user can set origin and destination postcodes.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Dual'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Country name'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Country name for Google maps API. Example: Italy. If set - used for both origin and destination. Otherwise customer MUST input country for destination or in both fields if dual mode is on!'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Fontsampler ID'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add ID of fontsampler you would like to use in this option'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Day/night mode'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Left/right panel position'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'View saved content'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'History of saved content'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Product general settings'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Delete content'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Non option variables'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Formula and conditional logic'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Save content'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Autosave'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'General Settings'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Price Settings'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'on'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'off'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Display custom options on the product page?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'This is the main option of the plugin. By choosing "off" you are entirely disabling the work of the plugin for this product. The plugin still may work for other your products, however.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable price calculation based on custom options?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Sometimes you just need to display custom options without using their values in a math formula as well as calculate the product price. Then just the custom options added to this product will be used only as an additional information in an order meta.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Important: this option will work only if you enable displaying of custom options!'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Use a special "calculate" button instead of instant price calculation?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable this option if you want to use "calculate" button and perform calculation on click on this button instead of instant price calculation after any options chosen/value defined.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable duplication of this product in the cart?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Cart item of this product can be duplicated in the cart if this option is enabled.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable inline editing of this product in the cart?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Cart item of this product will be possible to edit inline in the cart if this option is enabled. Inline editing mode means that form fields will be shown directly in the cart. Do not forget to enable inline editing for all or some options as it also works on per option basis!'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable editing of this product in the cart by returning to product page?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Cart item of this product will be possible to edit in the cart in "full" edit mode if this option is enabled. It means that a customer will be redirected to the product page where options\' values will be pre-filled with those from the cart item. A customer will be redirected to the cart after clicking both "Cancel" and "Update" buttons. The related cart item options\' values will be updated if "Update" button will be clicked.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable "silent validation" mode?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Removes validation error messages for all the required fields, but still correctly validates them; useful for preventing "this field is required" messages spam in the form field.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Custom quantity field'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'By default it is a standard WC qty field. But it also can be any Text Input based custom option. Important: WC original "sold individually" setting must be enabled so this setting could work!'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'WC qty field'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Sold individually?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Uni CPO uses WC original "sold individually" setting for hiding WC qty field only. Still, we need a possibility to restrict adding the same product twice to the cart even for Uni CPO enabled products. This is exactly what this setting does!'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Reset form button?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enable this option if you want to show "Reset all form" button'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Minimal price'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Set minimal possible price for the product regardless the calculated value by using the product custom formula.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],' Important: you still have to define a regular product price under General tab! Otherwise, this product will be considered as free.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Maximum price'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Set maximum possible price for the product. The calculated price will be compared with this value and ordering of the product will be disabled if the calculated price is bigger than this value. If "Text to display when ordering is disabled" setting is not empty, its value will be displayed in this case.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Text to display when ordering is disabled'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Every time you use a special word "disable" instead of actual formula, the product becomes disabled for ordering and the text below is displayed just under the product price. Leave it empty to disable the setting.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Price suffix'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Custom price tag suffix. If set, will be shown ONLY if the product ordering is disabled for any reason.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Price postfix'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Custom price tag postfix. If set, will be shown in any case.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Starting price'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Displays a starting price (marketing price) instead of "0.00" if any of required options is empty. Leave empty to disable the setting.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Price template for archives'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Custom price template to be displayed on archives. Special variables (<a href="https://moomoo-agency.gitbook.io/uni-cpo-4-documentation/usage/panel/general-settings" target="_blank"> the complete list of such vars </a>) and/or NOVs in triple curly braces can be used in the template.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Price template for archives during active sale'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'This the same as above, but this template will be chosen only during active sales campaign for this product.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Submit'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Main Formula & Formulas Conditional Logic'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Formula'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'This is a simple formula for your product. It will be applied if no rules are added or none of them are match.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Conditional Logic'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'It is also possible to use Formula Conditional Rules feature. First, enable it here and add some rules then.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Main formula'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Available variables:'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Controls:'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add Rule'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Remove All'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Fetch the rule'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Non Option Variables'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'NOVs are variables without direct connection to any options.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Wholesale'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Enabling this functionality will make it possible to set different value/formula on per user role basis'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Controls'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Please select...'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add/Change attachment'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Remove attachment'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Repeat'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Position'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Attachment'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Size'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Synced, ID#{{- data.pid }}'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Unsync'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Not synced'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Connect'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Fetch data'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Save data'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Add'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Make default?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Exclude?'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Title'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Value'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Label'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Price / Rate (optional)'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'CSS Class (optional)'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Description (optional)'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Colour (optional)'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Optional! Is used as a suboption image as well as can be used as the one that replaces the main product image'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Alt Image'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Optional! Is used ONLY as the one that replaces the main product image'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'when is required'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'when type is invalid'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'for any custom validation'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Save changes'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Edit'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Edit (inline)'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Product Options and Price Calculation Formulas for WooCommerce – Uni CPO'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'https://builderius.io/cpo'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'Provides an opportunity to add extra product options with the possibility to calculate the price based on the chosen options and using custom maths formula!'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'MooMoo Agency'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'http://moomoo.agency'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]],'4.9.47'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['uni-cpo',1]]]];
